Text: FW Initial Outline for Report of the Electric and Natural G as Marketing CommitteeDOC Original Message From Seegers Jay Sent Monday November PM To Murphy Harlan Haskell Mark Hodge Jeff Miller Mark Osteen Randy Runnels David Hoefling Wade Vrana Paul Subject Initial Outline for Report of the Electric and Natural Gas Marketing CommitteeDOC This is a rough outline for our Report for the Year in Review Please plan to participate on a brief conference call on Monday November at am CT to discuss the outline and allocate writing responsibilities Initial Outline for Report of the Electric and Natural Gas Marketing CommitteeDOC Callin Number Code Please let Harlan Murphy know at if you are unable to participate on the call Thanks Jay CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information in this email may be confidential andor privileged This email is intended to be reviewed by only the individual or organization named above If you are not the intended recipient or an authorized representative of the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any review dissemination or copying of this email and its attachments if any or the information contained herein is prohibited If you have received this email in error please immediately notify the sender by return email and delete this email from your system Thank You Initial Outline for Report of the Electric and Natural Gas Marketing CommitteeDOC
